              ],
              "free_text": [
                ") dE/dx, e counter telescope in",
                " connection with  a 100 by 100 channel analyser",
                "Two H-gas proport. Counter for dE/dx-analysis and",
                "silicon surface barrier counter for E-analysis"
              ]
            }
          ],
